video.title: Dicte
video.synopsis: A crime reporter starts a new life by returning to her hometown, where she finds herself at odds with the police when she tries to solve their cases.

episodes.synopsis: Dicte finds the body of a young woman who died of a C-section. Due to this macabre find, Dicte gets to know Inspector Wagner.
episodes.title: Personal - Part 1

episodes.synopsis: One summer night, Dicte sees a burning cart in the driveway of her neighbors. Inside the house, Inger Gravgård seems to have committed suicide.
